dev.lyze.gdxtinyvg.enums

Enum CommandType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CommandType>
      • dev.lyze.gdxtinyvg.enums.CommandType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<CommandType>

    public enum CommandType
extends java.lang.Enum<CommandType>
    TinyVG files contain a sequence of draw commands that must be executed in the defined order to get the final result. Each draw command adds a new 2D primitive to the graphic.

      DRAW_LINE_LOOP

      END_OF_DOCUMENT

      FILL_RECTANGLE
      This command fills a set of rectangles.
      OUTLINE_FILL_PATH
      This command combines the fill and draw path command into one.
      OUTLINE_FILL_POLYGON
      This command draws a filled polygon with an outline.
      OUTLINE_FILL_RECTANGLES
      This command draws several filled rectangles with an outline.
